  "page": "Bastard Born",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><i><b>Bastard Born</b></i> is an account of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Alyn_Velaryon\" title=\"Alyn Velaryon\">Alyn Velaryon</a>'s life written by <a href=\"/index.php/Rue\" title=\"Rue\">Rue</a>, who may or may not have been a <a href=\"/index.php/Septa\" title=\"Septa\">septa</a>, and may or may not have been one of the Oakenfist's paramours. According to <i>Bastard Born</i>, Lord Alyn accepted the sexual advances made by Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Aliandra_Martell\" title=\"Aliandra Martell\">Aliandra Martell</a>, which <i><a href=\"/index.php/Hard_as_Oak\" title=\"Hard as Oak\">Hard as Oak</a></i> refuted.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p><a href=\"/index.php/Archmaester\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Archmaester\">Archmaester</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Gyldayn\" title=\"Gyldayn\">Gyldayn</a> considers this account to be colorful, but unreliable.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bastard_Born&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oake